Spur has released a video of a white man physically threatening a woman in front of her children. The man was later seen grabbing the hand of the child but the mother pulled the child back from the man.The incident sparked a nationwide outrage. The incident was captured on a cellphone by another patron of the resturant who was at the restaurant the time it happened. On Wednesday Spur said they looked at the footage and said it was clear that the child had been mishandled.&nbsp;courtesy of EWN.com&nbsp;&nbsp;